467
00:20:06,571 --> 00:20:10,040
Before Moolisa, I used
to say it's just beef.

468
00:20:10,042 --> 00:20:13,476
- I couldn't have been
more wrong.
- [ Dog Barks Twice ]

469
00:20:13,478 --> 00:20:15,845
Cows are living creatures
with beautiful hair...

470
00:20:15,847 --> 00:20:19,716
and soft brown eyes,
soft mouths.

471
00:20:19,718 --> 00:20:20,584
Whoo!

472
00:20:20,586 --> 00:20:23,653
And also they are beef.

473
00:20:23,655 --> 00:20:25,522
They're the full package.

474
00:20:25,524 --> 00:20:28,391
Does that make me
a hypocrite to say that?

475
00:20:28,393 --> 00:20:30,594
[ Randy ]
Yes.
No, it doesn't, Randy.

476
00:20:30,596 --> 00:20:32,462
Or if it does,

477
00:20:32,464 --> 00:20:33,697
I can live with that.

478
00:20:33,699 --> 00:20:37,867
I present our
hundred-thousandth burger.

479
00:20:38,669 --> 00:20:41,504
100,000th burger!

480
00:20:41,506 --> 00:20:42,973
All right!

481
00:20:42,975 --> 00:20:44,407
Right. Undo the banner.

482
00:20:44,409 --> 00:20:48,445
Bob's Burger!
100,000! All right!

483
00:20:48,447 --> 00:20:50,347
Hooray!
Do the banner.

484
00:20:50,349 --> 00:20:53,450
Here's the banner.
Here comes the banner.

485
00:20:53,452 --> 00:20:57,621
I humbly call this
the Rest in Peas burger.

486
00:20:57,623 --> 00:20:58,622
[ Linda Chuckling ]
Ha.

487
00:20:58,624 --> 00:21:01,992
Because it, uh, comes
with snap peas and carrots.
Thank you.

488
00:21:01,994 --> 00:21:04,327
All right, funeral people,

489
00:21:04,329 --> 00:21:06,396
it's time to party!

490
00:21:06,398 --> 00:21:09,399
♪ [ House ]

491
00:21:09,401 --> 00:21:12,435
♪ [ Continues ]

492
00:21:12,437 --> 00:21:14,004
♪ Gene machine

493
00:21:14,006 --> 00:21:15,839
♪ In the house

494
00:21:15,841 --> 00:21:17,807
♪ Get ready

495
00:21:17,809 --> 00:21:19,909
♪ To get it on

496
00:21:20,945 --> 00:21:23,913
♪ [ Continues ]

497
00:21:23,915 --> 00:21:25,882
[ Dog Barks ]

498
00:21:25,884 --> 00:21:29,319
♪ [ Continues ]

